1
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:34,520
=Lady Liberty=

2
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:37,940
=Episode 26=

3
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,440
I'm divorcing Lawyer Bei.

4
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,160
If everything goes smoothly,

5
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:20,422
it'll be finalized next week.

6
00:02:20,555 --> 00:02:21,520
You've heard, right?

7
00:02:22,440 --> 00:02:23,040
I have.

8
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,480
You must be happy.

9
00:02:29,244 --> 00:02:31,280
I don't think
your divorce is happening this fast

10
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:31,960
because of me.

11
00:02:33,040 --> 00:02:34,280
Maybe partly,

12
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,240
but not entirely.

13
00:02:36,040 --> 00:02:36,680
Because you

14
00:02:37,666 --> 00:02:39,240
don't have that kind of influence.

15
00:02:43,444 --> 00:02:44,720
Why did you ask to meet today?

16
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:46,720
Since you

17
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:48,560
love Bei Wenqi that much,

18
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:50,520
I'll give him to you.

19
00:02:50,688 --> 00:02:51,822
I don't want him anymore.

20
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,480
Since he's secondhand

21
00:02:54,640 --> 00:02:55,320
used by me,

22
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:56,520
I should at least tell you

23
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:57,720
how to deal with him, right?

24
00:02:59,911 --> 00:03:01,466
You have quite a sense of humor.

25
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:03,840
I've known about you all along.

26
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,240
Before you,

27
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:09,000
there were other young girls
he flirted with.

28
00:03:09,422 --> 00:03:10,711
Usually, once I stepped in,

29
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,720
he backed off.

30
00:03:12,440 --> 00:03:13,920
But this time,

31
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:16,880
he put in too much time

32
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:18,520
and effort.

33
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:22,400
That crossed my line.

34
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,440
Do you think

35
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:28,280
Zhang Yousen alone

36
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:30,680
could dig up everything

37
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:33,480
about the company you built together?

38
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:36,400
Even if he did,

39
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:37,560
do you think

40
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:39,720
he would dare threaten Lawyer Bei?

41
00:03:46,422 --> 00:03:48,240
You're all my seniors.
I should learn from you.

42
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,840
Don't say that.
We learn from each other.

43
00:03:49,933 --> 00:03:50,600
Come on. Get in.

44
00:03:51,288 --> 00:03:52,355
Give me a moment.

45
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,822
I want to say a few words to Lawyer Bei.

46
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:54,560
I'll come later.

47
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,120
You go ahead.

48
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:55,688
Alright.

49
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:00,920
See you later.

50
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:01,480
See you.

51
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,320
Are you saying

52
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:31,760
everything Zhang Yousen did

53
00:04:31,760 --> 00:04:32,640
was directed by you?

54
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:33,440
Most of it.

55
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,520
Some of it was his own initiative.

56
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:36,680
He did well.

57
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,920
He's capable.

58
00:04:38,577 --> 00:04:39,400
I also promised him

59
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:42,200
that if he dared
to break with Lawyer Bei,

60
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:45,040
I would give him more opportunities
to grow his career.

61
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:47,888
What about Lawyer Bei?

62
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:53,400
If I remember correctly,

63
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:56,280
his partners are currently negotiating

64
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:57,640
to withdraw their shares.

65
00:05:03,733 --> 00:05:05,911
How many people have decided
to follow you?

66
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:07,720
Including me, there are twelve.

67
00:05:08,044 --> 00:05:08,920
That's quite a number.

68
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:12,480
Decent, responsible, not overly harsh.

69
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:14,560
From an employee's perspective,

70
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:16,600
you're indeed a good boss.

71
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:24,280
When did my wife approach you

72
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,600
and convince you to be her informant?

73
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:30,320
If I remember right, you first met

74
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:32,880
at a company dinner last year.

75
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:34,120
Earlier than you think.

76
00:05:36,080 --> 00:05:38,280
You've only been at the firm
for less than two years.

77
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,000
I knew Mrs. Bei

78
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,720
two years ago.

79
00:05:43,400 --> 00:05:44,560
You're a big name.

80
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:46,360
So many people want to work under you

81
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,600
as junior associates.

82
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,440
Without connections,

83
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:51,320
how could

84
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:53,160
an ordinary law graduate like me

85
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,240
be so lucky

86
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:56,240
to join you right after graduation?

87
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:06,440
So from beginning to end,

88
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:09,840
you were my wife's informant?

89
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:13,640
I wouldn't call it that.

90
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:16,240
It was just an extra task.

91
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,480
My real goal

92
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,000
was to become a lawyer like you.

93
00:06:20,622 --> 00:06:22,488
I really hoped
nothing would happen to you,

94
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,120
so I could stay by your side

95
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,520
and learn from you.

96
00:06:27,200 --> 00:06:27,880
Who knew

97
00:06:28,111 --> 00:06:29,444
you would meet Zhou Mei?

98
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:32,240
And no one expected

99
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,466
I would end up liking her this much.

100
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:47,933
Thank you, Lawyer Bei.

101
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,560
I've learned a lot from you.

102
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,520
Alright, don't worry too much.

103
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:58,160
After all, he's still
a top lawyer out there.

104
00:06:58,400 --> 00:07:00,440
This won't break him.

105
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:01,920
It's just a small lesson at most.

106
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,640
He'll recover soon.

107
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,000
What will you do

108
00:07:11,444 --> 00:07:12,511
after the divorce?

109
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:13,360
Me?

110
00:07:20,555 --> 00:07:22,360
If I meet someone I like,
I'll be with him.

111
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:24,320
If not, I'll stay single.

112
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:26,000
I have my parents,

113
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:28,120
my own interests,

114
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,800
money, a car, a house,

115
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,080
a housekeeper, a driver,

116
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:31,960
and two dogs.

117
00:07:32,622 --> 00:07:33,240
That's enough.

118
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:35,040
Besides,

119
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,160
at my age,

120
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:39,000
I don't get angry anymore.

121
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:41,440
If a man won't behave,

122
00:07:42,577 --> 00:07:44,200
what's the point of keeping him?

123
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,960
Ma'am, would you like more tea?

124
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,200
No, thanks.

125
00:07:50,333 --> 00:07:51,360
I don't need anything.

126
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,240
Sure. Thank you.

127
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:56,640
Alright.

128
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:58,880
That's all

129
00:07:58,920 --> 00:07:59,600
I wanted to say.

130
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:01,440
I wish you happiness.

131
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:24,760
Mr. Gu Yan,

132
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,240
Mr. Fan is waiting for you.

133
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:27,177
Please come with me.

134
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:34,760
Mr. Fan.

135
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,360
Mr. Gu Yan's here.

136
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:39,880
Gu Yan.

137
00:08:40,400 --> 00:08:40,760
Mr. Fan,

138
00:08:40,866 --> 00:08:42,511
why aren't we meeting in your office?

139
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:45,280
Too many people are coming in and out

140
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:45,960
over there.

141
00:08:46,066 --> 00:08:46,880
This place is nice.

142
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:47,560
Quiet.

143
00:08:48,888 --> 00:08:50,400
Let me introduce a few colleagues.

144
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:52,440
Guo.

145
00:08:52,920 --> 00:08:53,560
Chang.

146
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:54,560
Mu.

147
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:55,600
Du.

148
00:08:55,920 --> 00:08:58,000
The Four Kings
of our content department.

149
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:00,680
Whether it's skill

150
00:09:00,880 --> 00:09:01,600
or experience,

151
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:04,080
they're the best in the industry.

152
00:09:06,920 --> 00:09:07,520
Of course,

153
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:09,360
only top-tier authors

154
00:09:09,920 --> 00:09:11,480
at our company

155
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,520
can get access to

156
00:09:13,622 --> 00:09:14,822
a support team like this.

157
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:15,720
Now,

158
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:18,920
you're the lucky one.

159
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,280
Lanxin.

160
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:25,320
Mr. Fan told me to come separately
from you.

161
00:09:25,355 --> 00:09:26,839
If people see us coming
and going together,

162
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:28,080
and Lin Zhanqiao hears about it,

163
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:28,920
that won't be good.

164
00:09:31,160 --> 00:09:31,640
Gu Yan,

165
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:34,600
your project, Drunk Old Friend,
with Zhanqiao,

166
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,880
should be wrapping up soon.

167
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:39,880
But your continuation
of Parting with Yan Dan at Yishui

168
00:09:39,880 --> 00:09:42,600
under the pen name Sansan

169
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:43,720
has only begun.

170
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,200
If there's any issue

171
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:46,520
with either project,

172
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:48,400
they can help you.

173
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,120
But...

174
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,320
once both projects are finished,

175
00:09:54,880 --> 00:09:55,520
would you

176
00:09:55,680 --> 00:09:58,640
consider signing
with Zhao Lanxin instead?

177
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:06,080
Mr. Fan invested in

178
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:07,560
Colorful Culture Media.

179
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:14,480
I have a long-term contract
with Lin Zhanqiao.

180
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:15,760
I'll handle that.

181
00:10:16,160 --> 00:10:16,720
How?

182
00:10:18,688 --> 00:10:20,311
You don't need to worry about that.

183
00:10:21,266 --> 00:10:22,488
I can't agree to this.

184
00:10:25,380 --> 00:10:27,760
Do you know who the person
you've always admired, Phantom Knight,

185
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:28,320
really is?

186
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:31,560
It's Lin Zhanqiao.

187
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:36,040
It was only after you gave me this file

188
00:10:36,177 --> 00:10:37,844
that my suspicions were confirmed.

189
00:10:37,888 --> 00:10:39,500
(Parting with Yan Dan at Yishui
Project Proposal)

190
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:41,420
Although Phantom Knight

191
00:10:41,430 --> 00:10:43,320
never finished
Parting with Yan Dan at Yishui,

192
00:10:43,488 --> 00:10:44,460
you know how authors are.

193
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:45,990
(Character chart and worldbuilding)
They usually plan character charts,

194
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:46,920
(of Parting with Yan Dan at Yishui)
story outlines,

195
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:48,920
and even the worldbuilding in advance.

196
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:51,560
You're Phantom Knight?

197
00:10:52,880 --> 00:10:53,960
I'm not.

198
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:57,480
After acquiring the rights to

199
00:10:58,200 --> 00:11:00,600
Parting with Yan Dan at Yishui,

200
00:11:01,880 --> 00:11:03,600
I met with Phantom Knight's
former editor

201
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:04,560
a few times,

202
00:11:04,911 --> 00:11:06,866
and that's when I started suspecting it.

203
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:08,840
But I think

204
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,960
since you admire Phantom Knight so much,

205
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:12,400
when you wanted to continue

206
00:11:12,400 --> 00:11:13,880
her unfinished novel,

207
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,560
she should've supported you.

208
00:11:15,880 --> 00:11:17,200
Instead of stopping you

209
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:18,560
for personal reasons,

210
00:11:18,560 --> 00:11:21,030
especially when this project
could bring both fame and money.

211
00:11:21,044 --> 00:11:23,800
If she truly trusted you,

212
00:11:24,111 --> 00:11:25,755
she should've told you the truth.

213
00:12:01,955 --> 00:12:02,960
Sir, a haircut, please.

214
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:03,720
Sure.

215
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:05,760
Thank you.

216
00:12:07,560 --> 00:12:07,960
Mr. Zhang.

217
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:09,360
Alright. Thank you.

218
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:09,920
Congratulations.

219
00:12:09,920 --> 00:12:11,480
- Share the good luck with us.
- Thank you.

220
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:12,360
Ms. Lin.

221
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:12,955
Have one, too.

222
00:12:13,044 --> 00:12:14,910
- You're waiting for Wang Hai?
- Congratulations.

223
00:12:14,920 --> 00:12:16,080
I went looking for him at his place,
but he wasn't there.

224
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:17,080
I'll wait for him here.

225
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:19,720
I saw a car pick him up this morning.

226
00:12:24,977 --> 00:12:25,822
Wedding candy.

227
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:26,560
It's ours.

228
00:12:27,760 --> 00:12:28,640
You two got married?

229
00:12:29,155 --> 00:12:30,400
We just registered.

230
00:12:30,444 --> 00:12:32,311
We checked the date.
Today's is a lucky one.

231
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,480
Congratulations.

232
00:12:42,280 --> 00:12:43,840
Wang Hai's the only single one now.

233
00:12:44,040 --> 00:12:45,600
Ms. Lin, please be nice to him.

234
00:12:45,960 --> 00:12:46,480
Of course.

235
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:47,840
Wang Hai's in demand right now.

236
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:49,240
If you don't value him,

237
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,777
someone else might snatch him away.

238
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:53,560
Judging by the rankings,

239
00:12:53,920 --> 00:12:54,920
he's doing really well.

240
00:12:55,311 --> 00:12:57,120
But that doesn't mean
he has no competition.

241
00:12:57,200 --> 00:12:58,080
You mean He Han?

242
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,480
Isn't he already finished?

243
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:01,440
There's another newcomer.

244
00:13:01,560 --> 00:13:02,160
Sansan.

245
00:13:02,311 --> 00:13:03,860
I think you've heard of this name.

246
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:07,520
Sansan is...

247
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:08,320
Sansan...

248
00:13:08,400 --> 00:13:10,480
- No idea what they write.
- No idea who they are. Haven't heard.

249
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:11,622
- This name
- No clue.

250
00:13:11,666 --> 00:13:12,880
is kind of random though.

251
00:13:12,880 --> 00:13:13,680
Yeah, pretty random.

252
00:13:13,680 --> 00:13:14,520
Three times three is nine.

253
00:13:14,560 --> 00:13:15,200
Doesn't sound...

254
00:13:15,240 --> 00:13:16,222
Why's everyone here?

255
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:17,800
You're back.

256
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:18,760
Sorry.

257
00:13:18,880 --> 00:13:20,111
Had to go out for something.

258
00:13:24,920 --> 00:13:25,560
We got married.

259
00:13:25,800 --> 00:13:26,740
Here's a gift for you.

260
00:13:27,880 --> 00:13:28,520
Congratulations.

261
00:13:31,800 --> 00:13:32,640
You guys carry on.

262
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:34,466
Come by for dinner sometime tonight.

263
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:37,560
Let's go.

264
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:41,120
Were you surprised

265
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:42,040
they got married?

266
00:13:42,800 --> 00:13:43,800
When we write novels,

267
00:13:43,800 --> 00:13:45,360
the plot has to make sense.

268
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,866
Everything has to be built step by step.

269
00:13:46,920 --> 00:13:48,120
Otherwise, readers say

270
00:13:48,120 --> 00:13:49,120
we're making things up.

271
00:13:49,622 --> 00:13:51,488
They'll curse us out.
Nobody will read it.

272
00:13:52,520 --> 00:13:53,440
But in real life,

273
00:13:53,933 --> 00:13:55,680
you've already been punched in the face

274
00:13:55,760 --> 00:13:56,760
before you're even ready.

275
00:13:57,920 --> 00:13:59,320
If the punch you're talking about

276
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:00,560
is about San Mei,

277
00:14:01,560 --> 00:14:03,320
then you deserved it.

278
00:14:05,244 --> 00:14:07,160
What if you were the one who punched me?

279
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:08,440
What do you mean?

280
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:09,920
Phantom Knight.

281
00:14:11,400 --> 00:14:11,920
Not me.

282
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,240
Tell me who it was.

283
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:20,280
You had the second half outline

284
00:14:20,280 --> 00:14:21,680
of Parting with Yan Dan at Yishui.

285
00:14:22,240 --> 00:14:23,840
You surely knew who Phantom Knight was.

286
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:26,160
That's why He Han

287
00:14:26,280 --> 00:14:27,520
shamelessly copied scenes

288
00:14:27,680 --> 00:14:29,160
from it.

289
00:14:29,880 --> 00:14:30,840
Because he had read

290
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:32,577
that unfinished, unpublished manuscript.

291
00:14:32,640 --> 00:14:34,400
Because he knew you were the author.

292
00:14:34,466 --> 00:14:35,920
You would never report him anyway.

293
00:14:36,222 --> 00:14:38,266
Otherwise, how would he dare
plagiarize it?

294
00:14:38,444 --> 00:14:39,466
Wouldn't he be afraid

295
00:14:39,488 --> 00:14:41,730
Phantom Knight would expose him
the moment it was published?

296
00:14:42,200 --> 00:14:43,040
If it wasn't you,

297
00:14:43,560 --> 00:14:44,920
then explain all this to me.

298
00:14:45,160 --> 00:14:46,400
I don't owe you an explanation.

299
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:48,066
You never trusted me in the first place.

300
00:14:48,111 --> 00:14:50,080
I've been trying to get closer to you
the whole time,

301
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:51,520
but you kept pushing me away.

302
00:14:51,520 --> 00:14:52,880
Gu Yan, trust goes both ways.

303
00:14:52,880 --> 00:14:54,511
It's always been one-sided between us.

304
00:14:55,888 --> 00:14:58,111
You want me to be completely loyal
to you.

305
00:14:58,960 --> 00:14:59,440
But you

306
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,880
keep holding things back.

307
00:15:02,022 --> 00:15:03,240
What you say and what you do

308
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:04,400
are two different things.

309
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:05,880
You know my room was

310
00:15:05,880 --> 00:15:07,520
full of traces of Phantom Knight.

311
00:15:08,240 --> 00:15:09,720
You know how much I admire her.

312
00:15:10,080 --> 00:15:10,880
But you acted like

313
00:15:10,880 --> 00:15:12,120
it had nothing to do with you.

314
00:15:12,880 --> 00:15:14,160
Why can't you tell me the truth?

315
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:15,800
Are you afraid I'd betray you?

316
00:15:15,844 --> 00:15:18,155
Mr. Fan bought the unfinished
Parting with Yan Dan at Yishui

317
00:15:18,311 --> 00:15:19,440
using all kinds of tactics

318
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:20,760
just to hype it up.

319
00:15:21,880 --> 00:15:23,440
You changed your name and followed him

320
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:24,920
and Zhan Lanxin to do the sequel,

321
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:26,320
seeking fame and profit.

322
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:27,400
What is that supposed to be?

323
00:15:27,640 --> 00:15:28,760
Give me an explanation.

324
00:15:29,600 --> 00:15:31,511
And you're here talking to me
about trust?

325
00:15:31,540 --> 00:15:32,840
Don't you think that's ridiculous?

326
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:34,160
You stopped trusting me first.

327
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:36,360
I don't owe you my trust.

328
00:15:36,840 --> 00:15:38,320
Trust has to be earned

329
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:39,400
little by little.

330
00:15:39,400 --> 00:15:40,320
But you trust He Han.

331
00:15:40,560 --> 00:15:41,920
Of course I trust him.

332
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:43,360
Because no matter what,

333
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:45,240
he's never done to me
what you've done.

334
00:15:45,320 --> 00:15:46,440
That's exactly why

335
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:48,280
there's always been a He Han between us.

336
00:15:48,280 --> 00:15:50,320
No matter what I do,
I can't get past him.

337
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:53,200
Whether in this industry or with you.

338
00:15:53,800 --> 00:15:55,080
That's why I wanted to continue

339
00:15:55,080 --> 00:15:56,000
Phantom Knight's novel.

340
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:57,100
If I wrote it well enough,

341
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:58,640
I could surpass him.

342
00:16:00,088 --> 00:16:01,880
But you wouldn't
let me touch the project.

343
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:04,600
Wasn't that just your selfishness?

344
00:16:07,333 --> 00:16:08,888
On your path to fame and success

345
00:16:09,160 --> 00:16:10,440
as a writer,

346
00:16:10,440 --> 00:16:12,311
I may be the only editor
you've ever met.

347
00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:14,520
But on my path as an editor,

348
00:16:14,520 --> 00:16:15,880
I've met countless authors

349
00:16:15,880 --> 00:16:17,000
like you.

350
00:16:18,720 --> 00:16:19,080
Yes.

351
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:20,911
When fame and profit are involved,

352
00:16:20,977 --> 00:16:22,320
people rush to seize the opportunity.

353
00:16:22,333 --> 00:16:23,660
There's nothing shameful about that.

354
00:16:23,688 --> 00:16:25,755
But don't stand here
using trust as an excuse.

355
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:29,040
So you're saying

356
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:31,600
I'm chasing fame and attention?

357
00:16:34,866 --> 00:16:36,444
Chasing fame and attention?

358
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:37,760
That sounds ugly.

359
00:16:39,320 --> 00:16:41,120
Call it ambition instead.

360
00:16:42,440 --> 00:16:43,480
Lin Zhanqiao, tell me.

361
00:16:44,720 --> 00:16:45,640
If I left you,

362
00:16:45,640 --> 00:16:46,640
would it hurt?

363
00:16:47,333 --> 00:16:48,560
If you stabbed me in the back,

364
00:16:50,088 --> 00:16:51,040
of course it would.

365
00:16:51,355 --> 00:16:52,720
Last time, when I left Shanghai

366
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:54,000
and stopped submitting chapters,

367
00:16:54,466 --> 00:16:56,777
if I never came back,
if I quit writing altogether,

368
00:16:57,266 --> 00:16:59,000
would you come find me
and ask me to return?

369
00:16:59,440 --> 00:16:59,880
I wouldn't.

370
00:17:10,160 --> 00:17:10,720
Done?

371
00:17:12,600 --> 00:17:13,480
My turn now.

372
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:15,440
Stop writing the sequel to

373
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:16,540
Parting with Yan Dan at Yishui

374
00:17:16,555 --> 00:17:17,755
under the name Sansan immediately,

375
00:17:18,244 --> 00:17:20,040
and cut all cooperation
with Zhao Lanxin.

376
00:17:20,720 --> 00:17:21,240
Do you agree?

377
00:17:21,400 --> 00:17:22,160
No.

378
00:17:23,320 --> 00:17:24,840
First, I never worked with Zhao Lanxin.

379
00:17:24,840 --> 00:17:25,240
Second,

380
00:17:26,066 --> 00:17:26,866
I'm not Sansan.

381
00:17:26,911 --> 00:17:29,150
I didn't do the sequel
to Parting with Yan Dan at Yishui.

382
00:17:29,760 --> 00:17:30,080
Fine.

383
00:17:31,800 --> 00:17:33,040
Remember what you said today.

384
00:17:41,700 --> 00:17:42,940
("Love alone could stretch across
thirty thousand chapters.")

385
00:17:42,940 --> 00:17:47,180
(The Heavenly Domain Falls,
written by Phantom Knight)

386
00:18:06,480 --> 00:18:06,840
Hello?

387
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:08,320
Off work yet?

388
00:18:09,133 --> 00:18:10,200
I'll pick you up.

389
00:18:10,533 --> 00:18:12,040
Let's have dinner together tonight

390
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:13,240
and celebrate.

391
00:18:14,520 --> 00:18:15,520
Let's celebrate

392
00:18:16,080 --> 00:18:16,960
my freedom.

393
00:18:32,644 --> 00:18:33,560
Is Zhou Mei back yet?

394
00:18:34,755 --> 00:18:36,688
I just asked her.
She said she just got off work.

395
00:18:36,880 --> 00:18:38,360
She should be on the way.

396
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:39,800
I'm sorry

397
00:18:39,800 --> 00:18:42,040
to ask Zhou Mei
to call you over after work.

398
00:18:42,920 --> 00:18:43,480
It's nothing.

399
00:18:44,120 --> 00:18:45,760
Should I bring the dishes out first?

400
00:18:45,760 --> 00:18:46,880
We can eat while we talk.

401
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,080
Let's wait for Zhou Mei.

402
00:18:48,280 --> 00:18:49,360
Ask her where she is.

403
00:18:49,640 --> 00:18:49,960
Okay.

404
00:18:54,720 --> 00:18:55,320
Ms. Lin,

405
00:18:55,377 --> 00:18:57,777
Zhou Mei has told me
about your situation on the phone.

406
00:18:57,880 --> 00:18:58,844
Here's the situation.

407
00:18:59,080 --> 00:18:59,920
If San Mei

408
00:18:59,920 --> 00:19:02,440
signed a contract with Zhao Lanxin
using a real ID,

409
00:19:02,440 --> 00:19:04,410
and the work is published
under the name of Sansan,

410
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:06,400
technically, we have no way to prove

411
00:19:06,600 --> 00:19:07,800
that Gu Yan ghostwrote it.

412
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:10,240
So you can't sue him

413
00:19:10,577 --> 00:19:11,733
for breach of contract.

414
00:19:11,880 --> 00:19:13,320
You mean he can keep writing,

415
00:19:13,320 --> 00:19:14,360
and we can't stop him?

416
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:15,640
In theory, yes.

417
00:19:16,480 --> 00:19:18,080
But this novel

418
00:19:18,080 --> 00:19:19,640
is pretty popular right now.

419
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:22,000
If he admits he ghostwrote it,

420
00:19:22,040 --> 00:19:22,960
then we can sue.

421
00:19:26,560 --> 00:19:27,640
These are the contracts

422
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:29,080
I signed with Gu Yan before.

423
00:19:29,840 --> 00:19:31,360
I'll need you to go through them.

424
00:19:31,880 --> 00:19:33,600
If he plans to break the contract

425
00:19:33,920 --> 00:19:35,040
or terminate it,

426
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:37,160
what should we prepare in advance?

427
00:19:41,377 --> 00:19:42,320
Did she reply to you?

428
00:19:42,800 --> 00:19:43,400
Not yet.

429
00:19:44,555 --> 00:19:45,920
It's fine. Let's wait a bit.

430
00:19:46,480 --> 00:19:47,760
I'll take a look at the contract.

431
00:19:47,920 --> 00:19:48,920
We'll eat later.

432
00:19:49,400 --> 00:19:50,160
I'll call her.

433
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:50,800
Okay.

434
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:00,280
Hello?

435
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:01,760
When are you coming back?

436
00:20:01,960 --> 00:20:02,920
Zhang Yousen is waiting.

437
00:20:03,960 --> 00:20:05,120
Something came up.

438
00:20:05,120 --> 00:20:06,177
You guys go ahead and eat.

439
00:20:06,600 --> 00:20:07,280
Hurry up.

440
00:20:16,840 --> 00:20:17,160
Mei.

441
00:20:19,022 --> 00:20:21,190
I'm not eating tonight.
I'll have a drink with you.

442
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:22,240
I have plans later.

443
00:20:23,440 --> 00:20:23,800
Alright.

444
00:20:24,400 --> 00:20:24,840
Let's go.

445
00:20:29,760 --> 00:20:30,160
Come.

446
00:20:30,560 --> 00:20:30,920
Huang.

447
00:20:30,920 --> 00:20:31,400
You're here?

448
00:20:31,560 --> 00:20:31,880
Come.

449
00:20:33,720 --> 00:20:34,560
Let me introduce you.

450
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:36,640
This is my best friend

451
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:37,560
and coursemate,

452
00:20:37,840 --> 00:20:38,280
Huang.

453
00:20:38,711 --> 00:20:39,480
This is Zhou Mei.

454
00:20:40,520 --> 00:20:42,440
Miss Zhou, nice to finally meet you.

455
00:20:42,920 --> 00:20:43,360
Hello.

456
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:46,440
Looks like Lawyer Bei

457
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:48,040
has mentioned me before.

458
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:49,200
Not just mentioned,

459
00:20:49,480 --> 00:20:51,280
he praises you a lot.

460
00:20:53,040 --> 00:20:53,440
Come.

461
00:20:53,644 --> 00:20:54,200
Have a seat.

462
00:20:54,320 --> 00:20:54,640
Come.

463
00:20:54,800 --> 00:20:55,200
Sit.

464
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:01,280
Before this,

465
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:03,760
I never introduced my friends to you.

466
00:21:04,320 --> 00:21:05,760
Now that I've just gotten divorced,

467
00:21:06,080 --> 00:21:08,160
I actually don't want people to know

468
00:21:08,600 --> 00:21:10,040
that I've moved on so quickly.

469
00:21:11,160 --> 00:21:12,400
But Huang is different.

470
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:15,720
I don't want people to see me

471
00:21:16,320 --> 00:21:18,000
as an abandoned, divorced old woman.

472
00:21:18,400 --> 00:21:19,000
So...

473
00:21:20,120 --> 00:21:22,320
the divorce was my decision.

474
00:21:23,044 --> 00:21:24,680
I didn't want to stay with him anymore.

475
00:21:26,160 --> 00:21:28,080
Back then, I chose to marry him.

476
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:30,440
My family and I helped him

477
00:21:30,440 --> 00:21:31,720
become who he is today.

478
00:21:31,920 --> 00:21:33,844
But I don't want
to live with him anymore.

479
00:21:35,120 --> 00:21:35,920
I'm older than him.

480
00:21:36,600 --> 00:21:37,440
After we got married,

481
00:21:38,120 --> 00:21:39,040
I suddenly realized

482
00:21:40,480 --> 00:21:41,680
I didn't like him that much.

483
00:21:42,600 --> 00:21:44,000
Huang is my closest friend.

484
00:21:44,160 --> 00:21:45,840
He knows about us.

485
00:21:46,880 --> 00:21:47,760
He's the only one.

486
00:21:48,920 --> 00:21:50,520
He's a bit impatient.

487
00:21:51,120 --> 00:21:52,360
I heard

488
00:21:52,640 --> 00:21:53,560
you rented a new place.

489
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:54,880
Really?

490
00:21:56,000 --> 00:21:56,680
I didn't know.

491
00:21:59,200 --> 00:22:01,080
I haven't contacted you
these past few days

492
00:22:01,280 --> 00:22:04,040
because I've been busy
with family and firm matters.

493
00:22:05,520 --> 00:22:05,880
Right,

494
00:22:06,480 --> 00:22:08,720
I rented a place in Cuiyun Phase 5.

495
00:22:09,080 --> 00:22:09,680
I think

496
00:22:10,377 --> 00:22:11,560
I'll stay there for now,

497
00:22:11,800 --> 00:22:14,311
and buy something later
when I find a suitable property.

498
00:22:16,333 --> 00:22:17,400
What about the office?

499
00:22:18,960 --> 00:22:20,360
Rick and I have talked it through.

500
00:22:21,066 --> 00:22:22,440
I'll stay in the original office,

501
00:22:22,560 --> 00:22:23,511
and he'll move out.

502
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:25,240
I let him decide

503
00:22:25,600 --> 00:22:26,280
everything else.

504
00:22:26,955 --> 00:22:28,844
Doesn't that mean you're taking a loss?

505
00:22:29,155 --> 00:22:31,380
You can lose people or money,
but never your reputation.

506
00:22:32,600 --> 00:22:33,840
Staying where I am

507
00:22:33,880 --> 00:22:35,533
means my credibility is still intact.

508
00:22:36,555 --> 00:22:38,880
I may be taking a small loss for now,

509
00:22:39,400 --> 00:22:40,680
but in the long run,

510
00:22:41,280 --> 00:22:42,600
I've protected my reputation.

511
00:22:44,960 --> 00:22:45,560
Miss Zhou,

512
00:22:45,680 --> 00:22:47,640
Lawyer Bei is very shrewd.

513
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:48,520
You should learn

514
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:49,840
from him.

515
00:22:51,266 --> 00:22:52,644
I've already seen it for myself.

516
00:23:01,440 --> 00:23:02,320
I'll head back myself.

517
00:23:02,488 --> 00:23:03,560
I'll give you a ride.

518
00:23:03,840 --> 00:23:04,320
No need.

519
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:05,920
Huang is still inside.

520
00:23:06,680 --> 00:23:07,360
It's not far.

521
00:23:07,520 --> 00:23:08,600
Twenty minutes round trip.

522
00:23:09,120 --> 00:23:10,120
Let him wait a bit.

523
00:23:11,133 --> 00:23:11,960
It's fine, really.

524
00:23:18,560 --> 00:23:19,680
What I owed you before,

525
00:23:20,644 --> 00:23:22,088
I want to repay it slowly.

526
00:23:26,960 --> 00:23:27,360
Let's go.

527
00:23:46,600 --> 00:23:48,120
Let's eat first. Don't wait for her.

528
00:23:54,440 --> 00:23:56,240
Maybe have some juice.

529
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:58,840
Zhou Mei's usually not this flaky.

530
00:23:58,955 --> 00:24:00,800
It's okay. You guys eat.
I'll get going first.

531
00:24:00,840 --> 00:24:01,820
I have something to take care of later.

532
00:24:01,840 --> 00:24:03,120
What do you have to do this late?

533
00:24:03,120 --> 00:24:04,320
Have a few bites before you go.

534
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:06,733
There's a lot of new business
at the firm I need to deal with.

535
00:24:06,760 --> 00:24:07,733
Ms. Lin, call me anytime.

536
00:24:09,320 --> 00:24:09,880
I'm sorry

537
00:24:09,880 --> 00:24:11,040
to trouble you with that.

538
00:24:12,200 --> 00:24:13,440
When Zhou Mei gets back,

539
00:24:13,440 --> 00:24:14,400
I'll have her call you.

540
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:14,960
Okay.

541
00:24:14,960 --> 00:24:15,911
- Bye.
- Thank you.

542
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:28,440
Hello?

543
00:24:29,200 --> 00:24:30,560
I'm downstairs. Coming up now.

544
00:24:43,422 --> 00:24:44,177
What's wrong?

545
00:24:44,680 --> 00:24:45,080
Nothing.

546
00:24:57,040 --> 00:24:57,680
I'm heading up.

547
00:25:11,520 --> 00:25:11,960
Zhou Mei.

548
00:25:21,120 --> 00:25:22,680
I waited for you for over two hours.

549
00:25:23,640 --> 00:25:25,000
So you were with Lawyer Bei.

550
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:26,977
He needed to see me
about something urgent.

551
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:29,000
Have you eaten?

552
00:25:30,044 --> 00:25:31,240
Do you want to come upstairs?

553
00:25:31,400 --> 00:25:32,000
No need.

554
00:25:32,840 --> 00:25:34,080
I've answered

555
00:25:34,222 --> 00:25:35,560
everything Lin Zhanqiao asked.

556
00:25:37,480 --> 00:25:37,880
Thank you.

557
00:25:37,880 --> 00:25:39,422
Was the urgent matter you mentioned

558
00:25:40,760 --> 00:25:41,640
Lawyer Bei

559
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:42,840
finalizing the divorce?

560
00:25:47,777 --> 00:25:49,160
Mrs. Bei told you, didn't she?

561
00:25:49,280 --> 00:25:51,280
The one thing
I didn't expect in all of this

562
00:25:52,120 --> 00:25:52,960
was that

563
00:25:52,960 --> 00:25:54,240
she would take the initiative

564
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:55,480
and firmly ask for a divorce.

565
00:25:55,840 --> 00:25:56,960
And she didn't push Lawyer Bei

566
00:25:56,960 --> 00:25:58,240
to a dead end either.

567
00:26:04,600 --> 00:26:06,520
Is Lawyer Bei asking you to be with him?

568
00:26:15,000 --> 00:26:16,440
If you get together with him,

569
00:26:16,440 --> 00:26:17,360
your mom will kill you.

570
00:26:26,080 --> 00:26:27,200
That's my own business.

571
00:26:28,577 --> 00:26:30,280
No matter what my relationship is
with him,

572
00:26:30,280 --> 00:26:31,800
I don't want anything to do with you.

573
00:26:32,577 --> 00:26:33,760
You're asking for too much.

574
00:26:34,680 --> 00:26:35,880
You want to bring him down,

575
00:26:35,880 --> 00:26:36,820
get yourself promoted,

576
00:26:36,830 --> 00:26:37,920
and have me be with you.

577
00:26:39,400 --> 00:26:40,920
How can everything go your way?

578
00:27:17,920 --> 00:27:19,360
Lawyer Bei has finalized the divorce.

579
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:28,920
You went to see him just now?

580
00:27:31,840 --> 00:27:32,760
Does that mean

581
00:27:33,520 --> 00:27:35,120
you're getting together?

582
00:27:39,511 --> 00:27:40,711
Why are you looking at me?

583
00:27:47,320 --> 00:27:48,280
If one day

584
00:27:49,520 --> 00:27:50,520
He Han told you

585
00:27:53,280 --> 00:27:54,600
he had fixed all his flaws,

586
00:27:56,800 --> 00:27:58,600
and there were no more issues
between you...

587
00:28:00,680 --> 00:28:01,800
Would you start over?

588
00:28:13,488 --> 00:28:15,444
Then he wouldn't be He Han anymore.

589
00:28:24,480 --> 00:28:25,680
So even if things change,

590
00:28:26,177 --> 00:28:27,844
people still won't end up together.

591
00:28:28,444 --> 00:28:29,511
And if nothing changes,

592
00:28:31,600 --> 00:28:33,066
they won't be together either.

593
00:28:36,160 --> 00:28:37,400
Your situation is different.

594
00:28:39,760 --> 00:28:40,280
Mei...

595
00:28:41,933 --> 00:28:43,160
Lawyer Bei is divorced now.

596
00:28:43,760 --> 00:28:45,840
He's single and has come back to you.

597
00:28:46,400 --> 00:28:48,120
Isn't that what you've been waiting for?

598
00:28:54,720 --> 00:28:55,280
To be honest,

599
00:28:58,760 --> 00:29:00,640
I don't know why I feel so nervous.

600
00:29:02,160 --> 00:29:03,000
He didn't say

601
00:29:04,533 --> 00:29:06,040
he wants to marry me right away,

602
00:29:07,920 --> 00:29:09,160
or that we'll be together.

603
00:29:11,960 --> 00:29:13,960
We just started seeing each other again.

604
00:29:25,200 --> 00:29:26,200
What you're nervous about

605
00:29:28,640 --> 00:29:30,480
isn't your relationship with Lawyer Bei.

606
00:29:33,920 --> 00:29:35,640
It's your relationship with your mom.

607
00:29:41,755 --> 00:29:43,000
Your mom probably can't accept

608
00:29:43,000 --> 00:29:44,320
that her daughter

609
00:29:45,800 --> 00:29:47,320
is playing the very role she hates most

610
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:50,440
in a marriage.

611
00:29:53,560 --> 00:29:55,600
Who you choose to be with
is your decision.

612
00:29:55,600 --> 00:29:57,577
What does it have to do with your mom?

613
00:29:58,440 --> 00:29:59,080
Besides,

614
00:29:59,480 --> 00:30:01,200
being with Lawyer Bei isn't a crime.

615
00:30:01,355 --> 00:30:02,911
She has no right to judge you.

616
00:30:04,920 --> 00:30:06,720
You shouldn't date
to make your mom happy.

617
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:12,160
And you shouldn't date
to get back at her either.

618
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:44,320
I recognized you right away.

619
00:30:46,240 --> 00:30:47,560
You're good-looking.

620
00:30:47,666 --> 00:30:48,680
When you're dressed up,

621
00:30:49,920 --> 00:30:51,680
you really look the part.

622
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:54,040
Looking the part has nothing to do
with appearance.

623
00:30:54,760 --> 00:30:55,680
How many trips today?

624
00:30:56,000 --> 00:30:56,520
Three.

625
00:30:57,120 --> 00:30:58,440
I had a drop-off near the hotel,

626
00:30:58,440 --> 00:30:59,355
so I came by to see you.

627
00:30:59,400 --> 00:30:59,720
Here.

628
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:03,400
You look fresh now.

629
00:31:04,120 --> 00:31:04,960
Give it a few days,

630
00:31:04,960 --> 00:31:06,555
and you won't care
about your image anymore.

631
00:31:06,600 --> 00:31:07,600
No way.

632
00:31:07,640 --> 00:31:08,640
I'm doing pretty well.

633
00:31:08,640 --> 00:31:10,400
Honestly, my temper
has never been this good.

634
00:31:10,720 --> 00:31:12,840
One small complaint,
and I get suspended for days.

635
00:31:13,360 --> 00:31:14,600
What hours are you working?

636
00:31:15,880 --> 00:31:16,800
I started at 8 PM.

637
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:18,160
Can't go over 12 hours.

638
00:31:18,577 --> 00:31:19,560
But the good thing is,

639
00:31:20,080 --> 00:31:21,920
if you hit twelve hours,
you make money.

640
00:31:22,000 --> 00:31:23,040
You sleep easily at night.

641
00:31:23,177 --> 00:31:23,977
Not like before,

642
00:31:24,000 --> 00:31:26,511
sometimes I would sit there for 12 hours
and not write a single word.

643
00:31:26,555 --> 00:31:27,444
No money, and no sleep.

644
00:31:28,711 --> 00:31:31,177
You don't know how tough it is
until you've been through it.

645
00:31:31,880 --> 00:31:34,400
You've received a new order.
Please confirm.

646
00:31:35,111 --> 00:31:36,360
I have an order. I need to go.

647
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:38,360
Alright. Go ahead.

648
00:31:38,560 --> 00:31:39,120
Drive safe.

649
00:31:39,240 --> 00:31:39,960
Okay. Bye.

650
00:31:40,360 --> 00:31:40,960
Take care.

651
00:31:47,320 --> 00:31:48,920
Don't you know your own situation?

652
00:31:49,140 --> 00:31:51,177
And you still went
and guaranteed for someone else?

653
00:31:51,400 --> 00:31:52,280
Now they've run off,

654
00:31:52,377 --> 00:31:53,280
and the debt's on you.

655
00:31:53,511 --> 00:31:55,644
How are the kid and I
supposed to live like this?

656
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:58,920
It has been 16 years.

657
00:31:59,600 --> 00:32:00,480
Since I married you,

658
00:32:00,480 --> 00:32:01,960
have you given me a single good day?

659
00:32:02,720 --> 00:32:04,200
We hired you

660
00:32:04,266 --> 00:32:05,840
because you could handle pressure well.

661
00:32:06,133 --> 00:32:08,400
But now you can't even deal
with something this small.

662
00:32:08,880 --> 00:32:10,720
Clients and your colleagues
are complaining.

663
00:32:11,688 --> 00:32:13,540
Maybe you should step back
from this project.

664
00:32:15,288 --> 00:32:16,360
The Oriental Pearl Tower

665
00:32:16,640 --> 00:32:18,360
is taller than it looks on TV.

666
00:32:18,440 --> 00:32:18,960
Right?

667
00:32:19,160 --> 00:32:19,600
Dad,

668
00:32:19,880 --> 00:32:20,800
if we go up there,

669
00:32:20,800 --> 00:32:22,120
can we touch the clouds?

670
00:32:22,320 --> 00:32:23,080
If you do,

671
00:32:23,160 --> 00:32:25,120
grab a couple for me, alright?

672
00:32:25,760 --> 00:32:26,600
One hour.

673
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,200
Three hours.

674
00:32:29,160 --> 00:32:31,320
I can understand if you don't reply.

675
00:32:33,080 --> 00:32:34,960
But no one is so busy that

676
00:32:34,960 --> 00:32:37,320
they can't send a single message
all day.

677
00:32:40,520 --> 00:32:42,240
You simply don't want to reply.

678
00:32:44,080 --> 00:32:44,440
Hello?

679
00:32:45,280 --> 00:32:45,880
You know what?

680
00:32:46,520 --> 00:32:48,040
I finally broke up with him.

681
00:32:49,960 --> 00:32:50,360
Yeah.

682
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:51,400
Great.

683
00:32:51,440 --> 00:32:52,560
Go pack your luggage.

684
00:33:10,400 --> 00:33:10,960
Thank you.

685
00:33:11,000 --> 00:33:11,440
Thank you.

686
00:33:15,488 --> 00:33:16,320
How have you been?

687
00:33:18,560 --> 00:33:19,200
It's me.

688
00:33:21,280 --> 00:33:22,000
Mr. He.

689
00:33:22,560 --> 00:33:24,022
Are you collecting real-life experience

690
00:33:24,040 --> 00:33:25,560
for your next novel

691
00:33:25,711 --> 00:33:26,955
about a ride-hailing driver?

692
00:33:27,111 --> 00:33:27,960
No, this is real life.

693
00:33:27,960 --> 00:33:29,120
I don't believe you.

694
00:33:29,240 --> 00:33:30,320
Why would I lie?

695
00:33:36,800 --> 00:33:38,000
You've changed a lot.

696
00:33:40,080 --> 00:33:41,000
Why are you here again?

697
00:33:41,777 --> 00:33:43,222
Got used to meeting people here.

698
00:33:44,840 --> 00:33:45,840
Come sit in the lobby.

699
00:33:45,840 --> 00:33:46,560
Let's talk.

700
00:33:46,840 --> 00:33:47,360
I can't.

701
00:33:47,480 --> 00:33:48,160
I need to work.

702
00:33:49,080 --> 00:33:49,680
Your car?

703
00:33:49,866 --> 00:33:51,555
Alright. We'll talk in your car.

704
00:33:57,560 --> 00:33:58,160
See you, Mr. He.

705
00:33:58,440 --> 00:33:58,800
See you.

706
00:34:03,560 --> 00:34:04,360
This...

707
00:34:04,920 --> 00:34:05,920
doesn't suit you.

708
00:34:06,760 --> 00:34:07,960
It suits the job.

709
00:34:10,022 --> 00:34:11,444
I've accepted the next ride.

710
00:34:11,533 --> 00:34:12,560
Six minutes to get there.

711
00:34:13,640 --> 00:34:15,280
You're punctual, huh?

712
00:34:16,040 --> 00:34:16,840
That's a good thing.

713
00:34:21,200 --> 00:34:22,400
So, what did you want to say?

714
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:26,080
I don't know how long
you'll keep driving,

715
00:34:26,080 --> 00:34:27,840
or when you'll go back to writing.

716
00:34:27,933 --> 00:34:30,600
I'm sure a lot of companies
have reached out to you lately.

717
00:34:32,600 --> 00:34:34,480
So I just wanted to tell you this.

718
00:34:34,480 --> 00:34:37,120
Don't go back to web novel for now.

719
00:34:37,160 --> 00:34:38,080
Wait a few months.

720
00:34:41,320 --> 00:34:42,000
What do you mean?

721
00:34:43,880 --> 00:34:45,240
The whole industry

722
00:34:45,240 --> 00:34:46,960
is about to go through
a major reshuffle.

723
00:34:47,680 --> 00:34:49,920
I mean the rules themselves
are going to change.

724
00:34:50,920 --> 00:34:53,280
Even an aircraft carrier

725
00:34:53,280 --> 00:34:54,640
as big as Dingqi

726
00:34:55,880 --> 00:34:57,000
could capsize.

727
00:34:58,240 --> 00:34:59,160
Are you behind this?

728
00:35:02,120 --> 00:35:04,200
I just know something.

729
00:35:06,160 --> 00:35:07,360
Thank you for the heads-up.

730
00:35:07,533 --> 00:35:09,120
Take your things. We're almost there.

731
00:35:12,960 --> 00:35:13,280
Alright.

732
00:35:14,280 --> 00:35:14,760
I'm off.

733
00:35:24,840 --> 00:35:25,320
Hello.

734
00:35:25,444 --> 00:35:26,920
Hello. The last four digits are 3931.

735
00:35:27,040 --> 00:35:27,600
Alright.

736
00:35:27,866 --> 00:35:29,240
Dida Ride Service at your service.

737
00:35:29,240 --> 00:35:31,066
Please fasten your seat belt.
We're setting off.

738
00:35:46,240 --> 00:35:46,760
(Thank you.)

739
00:36:01,450 --> 00:36:04,280
♪Like a drifting dandelion♪

740
00:36:08,500 --> 00:36:15,660
(Zhanqiao: I need to talk to you.
Call me when you're free.)

741
00:36:16,990 --> 00:36:19,860
♪When the rain comes, I hide♪

742
00:36:19,860 --> 00:36:21,760
(Dida E-Hailing Service)

743
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:23,022
Thank you. Have a good night.

744
00:36:24,510 --> 00:36:29,930
♪Even spring borrows its fragrance♪

745
00:36:33,180 --> 00:36:36,740
(Zhanqiao: I need to talk to you.
Call me when you're free.)

746
00:36:38,910 --> 00:36:45,140
♪Across fields of blooms,
a boat awaits me♪

747
00:36:46,940 --> 00:36:51,260
(Zhanqiao. Dida E-Hailing Service:
New order waiting.)

748
00:36:51,400 --> 00:36:52,900
(Didi Express Real-Time Ride Request)

749
00:36:53,020 --> 00:36:54,711
You've received a new passenger
on Dida

750
00:36:54,777 --> 00:36:56,280
with last four digits 0357.

751
00:36:56,480 --> 00:36:59,000
Please follow navigation
to the pickup point.

752
00:36:59,240 --> 00:37:00,280
Reminder.

753
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:01,480
Please don't drive while tired.

754
00:37:17,288 --> 00:37:17,950
You're back.

755
00:37:17,960 --> 00:37:18,280
Morning.

756
00:37:18,520 --> 00:37:19,000
Pretty good.

757
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:31,688
How do I look?

758
00:37:32,120 --> 00:37:32,840
New look.

759
00:37:33,120 --> 00:37:33,680
Feels strange?

760
00:37:35,520 --> 00:37:36,640
I came

761
00:37:37,480 --> 00:37:38,400
to ask you a favor.

762
00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:40,960
I appreciate it,

763
00:37:41,120 --> 00:37:42,560
but I can't help you right now.

764
00:37:49,200 --> 00:37:50,040
I'm here

765
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:53,000
about the game rights

766
00:37:53,160 --> 00:37:54,440
of your earlier novel, Tao Yao.

767
00:37:56,680 --> 00:37:58,520
The negotiations aren't going well.

768
00:37:58,920 --> 00:38:00,440
We have another meeting this afternoon.

769
00:38:01,080 --> 00:38:02,080
The boss

770
00:38:02,240 --> 00:38:03,400
happens to be your reader,

771
00:38:03,960 --> 00:38:04,600
so I was

772
00:38:05,720 --> 00:38:06,960
hoping you could vouch

773
00:38:07,280 --> 00:38:08,280
for me.

774
00:38:11,040 --> 00:38:12,240
Your company needs money.

775
00:38:12,760 --> 00:38:14,480
They're buying your rights
and paying you.

776
00:38:14,520 --> 00:38:15,680
Isn't that a good thing?

777
00:38:15,680 --> 00:38:16,720
Why can't you reach a deal?

778
00:38:17,133 --> 00:38:19,000
And why do you need me to vouch for you?

779
00:38:19,160 --> 00:38:21,150
If I get involved, am I supposed to sit
on the contract talks too?

780
00:38:21,160 --> 00:38:22,200
Maybe we'll even discuss

781
00:38:22,200 --> 00:38:23,520
a series.

782
00:38:23,600 --> 00:38:25,080
And then you'll tell me to quit driving

783
00:38:25,080 --> 00:38:26,920
and come back to writing.
Did I get it right?

784
00:38:26,930 --> 00:38:27,540
That's not it.

785
00:38:27,600 --> 00:38:29,422
Look, I'm going to sleep this afternoon,

786
00:38:29,560 --> 00:38:30,680
same as this morning.

787
00:38:31,080 --> 00:38:32,480
Morning or afternoon,

788
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:33,360
or anything,

789
00:38:33,440 --> 00:38:34,200
I'm not going.

790
00:38:34,520 --> 00:38:35,040
Got it?

791
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:44,120
Close the door on your way out.
Thank you.

792
00:39:14,120 --> 00:39:15,840
This is the last time

793
00:39:16,360 --> 00:39:17,640
I'm coming here to talk about

794
00:39:18,120 --> 00:39:18,720
this project.

795
00:39:20,400 --> 00:39:21,200
Let me be clear.

796
00:39:23,600 --> 00:39:25,800
This novel isn't suitable
for a game adaptation.

797
00:39:26,560 --> 00:39:27,760
None of He Han's works

798
00:39:27,760 --> 00:39:29,244
are suitable for game adaptations.

799
00:39:31,066 --> 00:39:32,200
I swear I'm telling the truth.

800
00:39:33,160 --> 00:39:34,880
I started this project because

801
00:39:35,520 --> 00:39:37,200
it means something to me.

802
00:39:38,600 --> 00:39:39,680
How do I put it?

803
00:39:40,040 --> 00:39:41,880
A kind of admiration for his work,
you know?

804
00:39:44,680 --> 00:39:45,880
Based on what we discussed

805
00:39:45,880 --> 00:39:46,840
in the last meeting,

806
00:39:47,155 --> 00:39:48,380
we've sent the revised proposal

807
00:39:48,400 --> 00:39:50,240
to you and your team.

808
00:39:50,555 --> 00:39:51,422
I haven't read it.

809
00:39:51,533 --> 00:39:52,777
Neither have they.

810
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:55,520
There's no need. We'll
handle the proposal ourselves.

811
00:39:55,560 --> 00:39:56,511
No need to trouble you.

812
00:39:57,240 --> 00:39:57,920
We're building on

813
00:39:57,920 --> 00:39:59,600
a few key directions we believe in,

814
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:01,240
and refining them further.

815
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:01,800
Ms. Lin,

816
00:40:03,040 --> 00:40:04,840
what you need to confirm now

817
00:40:05,800 --> 00:40:06,640
is the price.

818
00:40:06,800 --> 00:40:08,040
What we need to establish is

819
00:40:08,155 --> 00:40:10,511
to build gameplay around
Tao Yao's characters as the core,

820
00:40:10,800 --> 00:40:12,360
create an experience

821
00:40:12,360 --> 00:40:13,080
that fits it,

822
00:40:14,200 --> 00:40:15,680
and convey its unique essence.

823
00:40:16,000 --> 00:40:18,440
Not just take its story

824
00:40:18,755 --> 00:40:20,480
and slap a new skin onto your Wildfire.

825
00:40:21,680 --> 00:40:22,160
Ms. Lin,

826
00:40:23,800 --> 00:40:24,560
to show

827
00:40:24,960 --> 00:40:26,280
our sincerity,

828
00:40:27,560 --> 00:40:29,880
I'm willing to raise the licensing fee

829
00:40:30,622 --> 00:40:31,760
by another five percent.

830
00:40:31,960 --> 00:40:33,280
I'll stand by my condition.

831
00:40:34,200 --> 00:40:35,080
Your game's storyline

832
00:40:35,920 --> 00:40:37,320
must be approved by Chenxing.

833
00:40:37,533 --> 00:40:38,600
That's not possible.

834
00:40:43,466 --> 00:40:44,622
Then let's forget it.

835
00:40:46,200 --> 00:40:46,960
Forget...

836
00:40:47,720 --> 00:40:48,160
Forget it?

837
00:40:49,160 --> 00:40:49,920
Are you saying

838
00:40:50,933 --> 00:40:51,840
you're not selling?

839
00:40:54,520 --> 00:40:55,160
I'm not selling.

840
00:41:02,266 --> 00:41:03,080
You can't do that.

841
00:41:03,266 --> 00:41:05,140
You're basically saying
in front of your employees

842
00:41:05,155 --> 00:41:06,680
that the company
is about to go under

843
00:41:06,680 --> 00:41:08,050
and they're going to lose their jobs.

844
00:41:08,060 --> 00:41:09,155
What kind of boss does that?

845
00:41:09,155 --> 00:41:10,360
That's completely irresponsible.

846
00:41:10,360 --> 00:41:12,400
Every industry has its own standards.

847
00:41:22,400 --> 00:41:23,840
Take down their contact details.

848
00:41:24,955 --> 00:41:26,222
If the company goes under,

849
00:41:26,320 --> 00:41:27,920
we can recruit them.

850
00:41:28,022 --> 00:41:29,288
They're welcome to come to us.

851
00:41:29,360 --> 00:41:31,480
Working under a boss like this
is indeed the worst luck.

852
00:41:31,888 --> 00:41:33,200
Good thing you've met me.

853
00:41:35,200 --> 00:41:35,640
Ms. Lin,

854
00:41:36,720 --> 00:41:37,920
if you change your mind,

855
00:41:38,400 --> 00:41:39,040
call me

856
00:41:40,440 --> 00:41:41,120
tonight.

857
00:42:21,240 --> 00:42:22,240
I'm sorry.

858
00:42:23,777 --> 00:42:25,644
All your hard work these past few months

859
00:42:26,320 --> 00:42:27,880
was for nothing.

860
00:42:36,160 --> 00:42:36,600
Ms. Lin,

861
00:42:37,400 --> 00:42:38,120
I'm with you.

862
00:42:39,760 --> 00:42:41,080
Whether as someone in the industry

863
00:42:41,360 --> 00:42:42,680
or as a fan of Mr. He Han,

864
00:42:43,066 --> 00:42:44,400
I think you made the right call.

865
00:42:48,480 --> 00:42:49,360
I made the proposal.

866
00:42:49,688 --> 00:42:52,422
I believe we can't lose our principles
no matter how tight things get.

867
00:42:58,560 --> 00:42:59,000
Ms. Lin,

868
00:42:59,680 --> 00:43:01,400
can I have a word with you?

869
00:43:05,921 --> 00:43:07,041
(I've been thinking.)

870
00:43:08,321 --> 00:43:11,601
(Everyone's most comfortable level of intimacy)

871
00:43:12,361 --> 00:43:19,691
(is probably different.)

872
00:43:20,691 --> 00:43:22,441
♪If the sky♪

873
00:43:22,951 --> 00:43:24,351
♪And the sea♪

874
00:43:24,891 --> 00:43:26,601
♪Turned upside down♪

875
00:43:28,161 --> 00:43:30,091
♪If a swimming fish♪

876
00:43:30,491 --> 00:43:33,881
♪Fell in love with a flying bird♪

877
00:43:35,651 --> 00:43:37,621
♪If back then♪

878
00:43:37,981 --> 00:43:42,391
♪We had never let go♪

879
00:43:42,991 --> 00:43:49,271
♪We wouldn't be lost in the crowd♪

880
00:43:50,391 --> 00:43:52,541
♪We met in a thirteenth month♪

881
00:43:52,541 --> 00:43:54,411
♪Held each other in a fifth season♪

882
00:43:54,591 --> 00:43:57,031
♪And found our way back whole♪

883
00:43:57,871 --> 00:44:00,041
♪So let this surging love♪

884
00:44:00,041 --> 00:44:04,471
♪Rise like tides that never fall♪

885
00:44:05,371 --> 00:44:07,551
♪If we're caught in a pouring rain♪

886
00:44:07,551 --> 00:44:08,641
♪That's alright♪

887
00:44:09,181 --> 00:44:09,931
♪If we're buried♪

888
00:44:09,931 --> 00:44:12,631
♪By passing years all the better♪

889
00:44:12,891 --> 00:44:15,071
♪At least we still can keep♪

890
00:44:15,251 --> 00:44:19,671
♪This one eternal photograph♪

891
00:44:35,431 --> 00:44:37,721
♪We're on misaligned tracks♪

892
00:44:37,721 --> 00:44:39,481
♪Running in opposite ways♪

893
00:44:39,601 --> 00:44:42,071
♪Searching all along the way♪

894
00:44:42,871 --> 00:44:45,031
♪For the fire of our younger hearts♪

895
00:44:45,221 --> 00:44:50,131
♪And the beauty lost in time♪

896
00:44:50,131 --> 00:44:53,651
♪This time don't lose each other again♪

897
00:44:53,891 --> 00:44:54,861
♪Only after loss♪

898
00:44:54,861 --> 00:44:57,491
♪Do we learn what truly matters most♪

899
00:44:57,901 --> 00:45:00,261
♪In another time and space♪

900
00:45:00,261 --> 00:45:01,821
♪We'll stay and walk together♪

901
00:45:01,821 --> 00:45:04,651
♪Till we grow old♪

902
00:45:05,611 --> 00:45:07,901
♪But still the sky will never♪

903
00:45:07,901 --> 00:45:10,571
♪Turn with the sea♪

904
00:45:13,091 --> 00:45:15,501
♪But still a swimming fish won't♪

905
00:45:15,501 --> 00:45:20,711
♪Fall in love with a flying bird♪
